data.description: This incredible newer construction home is nestled in the quiet Brookstone Ridge neighborhood with a large open floor plan with many attractive features for an affordable price! The home features 4 bedrooms, and 2 bathrooms, and was built in 2021 with all the up-to-date features and materials. The spacious kitchen has stainless steel appliances, lots of cabinet space for storage, a great-sized pantry, and a massive kitchen island with a built-in sink looking over the living room. The primary suite is a haven with warm natural light and a large bathroom featuring a standalone shower, double vanity, and massive closet space. The backyard provides great privacy with it's good size and being fully fenced in. Located right off the turnpike with a ton of shops, restaurants, grocery stores nearby, and only 15 minutes from downtown OKC.
